Package: kludgenudger
Title: support for Bruno Crotman's thesis about kludges in software development
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Bruno",
           family = "Crotman",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "crotman@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3102-6310"))
Description: Extract possible kludges com source code using PMD alerts. Categorize alerts in fixed, open and new.
